## 🚀 Featured Projects

### 🤟 Sign Language Gesture Recognition
**Real-time American Sign Language recognition system**
- Built with: **Python** | **OpenCV** | **MediaPipe** | **Computer Vision**
- 20+ gesture recognition with real-time inference (~24 FPS)
- 21-point hand tracking for accurate landmark extraction
- Modular pipeline architecture for production deployment
- [View Repository →](https://github.com/SaiprakashBalamurali)

### 📩 SMS Spam Detection
**End-to-end NLP classification pipeline**
- Built with: **Python** | **Pandas** | **NLTK** | **Scikit-learn** | **TF-IDF**
- Processed 5,574 labelled SMS messages with precision preprocessing
- Achieved **97.2% accuracy** and **96.8% F1-score**
- Benchmarked multiple classification approaches
- [View Repository →](https://github.com/SaiprakashBalamurali)

### 📊 Blinkit Sales Intelligence Dashboard
**Interactive executive retail analytics dashboard**
- Built with: **Power BI** | **DAX** | **Data Modelling**
- Analysed 8,500+ retail transactions
- Designed KPI cards, slicers, and analytical views
- Transformed raw retail data into actionable insights
- [View Repository →](https://github.com/SaiprakashBalamurali)

### 👕 AI-Based Smart Outfit Recommendation System
**Content-based recommendation engine with web UI**
- Built with: **Recommendation System** | **Cosine Similarity** | **Responsive Design**
- Personalized outfit suggestions based on occasion, style, and colour
- End-to-end development from ML logic to deployment
- [View Live Project →](https://saiprakash-s-portfolio.vercel.app)

